  "solicitation": "Beyond the edge of known space lies the Void, a cosmic maelstrom where reality frays. KAI, a solitary voidrunner, navigates these treacherous currents, delivering illicit cargo and seeking answers to a past she can’t outrun. But a ghost from her shattered memory emerges, holding a secret that could unravel the very fabric of her universe. Now, Kai must race against a galactic conspiracy to uncover the truth before the Void consumes everything. Strap in for a high-octane thrill ride through the darkest corners of the cosmos!"
